data.shortDescription: A cozy dining table that is perfect for afternoon luncheons. It fits in with any home's decor with its natural styling, while comfortably seating 4.
A versatile patio table that is suitable for the outdoors.  Its dark styling perfectly complements any porch, patio, or deck, either on its own, or while inside a gazebo.
A modern table that is perfect for serving your guests an after-dinner coffee, tea, and dessert.
A compact pub table that provides modern styling and seating for your kitchen or basement bar.
